               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Ketoconazole Shampoo, 2% is a red-orange liquid and is available as follows:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>4 fl. oz. (120 mL) nonbreakable plastic bottle (NDC 53217-<content styleCode="bold">015</content>-01) </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20131002"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="LINK_fb2d66b0-5f5f-4cbc-984a-639678742a2e">
